+- AFF access tail shows matching `GET /aff/api/external/session` at `27/Mar/2026:06:15:38 -0400`, `06:15:43`, and `06:15:44`: [`artifacts/aff-boot.access.tail.txt`](artifacts/aff-boot.access.tail.txt)
 
